  "title": "secretx umbrella: implement from_uri dispatch",
  "description": "Implement the from_uri(uri: &str) -> Result<Arc<dyn SecretStore>, SecretError> free function in secretx/src/lib.rs. Parse the URI scheme (the part before ://) and dispatch to the appropriate backend crate via #[cfg(feature)] match arms. This is the ONLY location in the workspace that uses #[cfg(feature)]. Return SecretError::InvalidUri with the missing feature name for backends not compiled in. Re-export secretx_core::{SecretValue, SecretError, SecretStore, SigningBackend, SigningAlgorithm}. Unit tests: from_uri dispatches correctly for each compiled-in scheme; returns InvalidUri for unknown scheme. Depends on all backend crates.",
